      /* PrepTransactionData.do */

/** @author Allcott and Taubinsky */

/* Summer Data */
if `Summer'==1 {

** Keep only the lightbulb part of transactions
keep if assortment=="COMMERCIAL FLUORESCENT"|assortment=="COMPACT FLUORESCENT BULBS"|assortment=="RESIDENTIAL FLUORESCENT"|assortment=="LIGHT BULBS-GENERAL PURPOSE"|assortment=="INDOOR FLOODS"|assortment=="LIGHT BULBS-DECORATIVE"|assortment=="OUTDOOR FLOODS"|assortment=="LED ACCENT LIGHTS"|assortment=="LED RETROFIT LIGHT BULBS"|assortment=="NIGHTLIGHTS"|assortment=="LANDSCAPE BULBS"|assortment=="LIGHT BULBS-SPECIALTY"


drop  storenumber  couponevent 
rename mastersale TransactionNum
rename barcode CouponBarcode
rename firstname FirstName
rename postalcode Zip
rename date TransactionDate
rename assortment AssortmentName
rename totalqty SalesUnits
rename  totalsaleamount SalesDollars

gen Purchased = (SalesDollars>0&SalesDollars!=.)

}

/* Non-Summer Data */ 
if `Summer'==0 {


* Name variables
rename ideas42brooklyn TransactionNum
rename v2 CouponBarcode
rename v3 FirstName
rename v4 Zip
rename v5 TransactionDate
rename v6 TransactionHour
rename v9 AssortmentNum
rename v10 AssortmentName
rename v11 PriceChangeCode
rename v12 SalesUnits
rename v13 SalesDollars

drop if _n<=8
destring TransactionNum Zip TransactionHour AssortmentNum SalesUnits, replace force
destring CouponBarcode, replace force 
destring SalesDollars, replace force ignore("$")

gen Purchased = (SalesDollars>0&SalesDollars!=.)


}


/* Notes on bulb types */
* Indoor floods are moderately substitutable.
* Decorative bulbs are substitutable to different degrees. Moderately substitutable.
* Outdoor floods are moderately substitutable.
* Specialty bulbs are often appliance bulbs that are not substitutable.

gen Fluorescent_Units = cond(AssortmentName=="COMMERCIAL FLUORESCENT"|AssortmentName=="COMPACT FLUORESCENT BULBS"|AssortmentName=="RESIDENTIAL FLUORESCENT",SalesUnits,0)
gen CFL_Units = cond(AssortmentName=="COMPACT FLUORESCENT BULBS",SalesUnits,0)
gen Incandescent_Units = cond(AssortmentName=="LIGHT BULBS-GENERAL PURPOSE",SalesUnits,0)
gen IndoorFlood_Units = cond(AssortmentName=="INDOOR FLOODS",SalesUnits,0)
gen Decorative_Units = cond(AssortmentName=="LIGHT BULBS-DECORATIVE",SalesUnits,0)
gen OutdoorFlood_Units = cond(AssortmentName=="OUTDOOR FLOODS",SalesUnits,0)
gen LED_Units = cond(AssortmentName=="LED ACCENT LIGHTS"|AssortmentName=="LED RETROFIT LIGHT BULBS",SalesUnits,0)
gen Other_Units = cond(AssortmentName=="NIGHTLIGHTS"|AssortmentName=="LANDSCAPE BULBS"|AssortmentName=="LIGHT BULBS-SPECIALTY",SalesUnits,0)

foreach t in CFL Fluorescent Incandescent IndoorFlood Decorative OutdoorFlood LED Other {
	gen `t'_Dollars = SalesDollars*(`t'_Units!=0)
	gen `t'_Purchased = (`t'_Units!=0)
}
